data.description: This cozy cape is just the one you have been waiting for!  Farmers porch is great for a morning coffee or afternoon cup of tea. This home has it all!  Beautifully updated and maintained over the past 8 years, pride of ownership truly shows.  Two large bedrooms upstairs with a full remodeled bath.  The main level boasts a living room with an open feel to the kitchen and another 2 bedrooms (one currently being used as the dining room), one with pellet stove that will stay, and another full remodeled bath.  Plenty of storage in the basement and a one car garage.  Large open back yard with an additional 2.3 acre lot that will be included in sale.  Nothing to do but move in!  Furniture and decor are negotiable.  Don't miss open house Sunday February 18th 11-1:30pm.
